title: Mary Wickes and Philip Baker Hall

description: Matthew Socey dips into the archives and relays his chat with author Steve Taravella, who wrote a biography on Mary Wickes (her birthday was this week) and ends the show with a tribute to actor Philip Baker Hall. There's also a lot in between.
